column5: Have a great trip to Sessi, never been there but hear good things about it. With it being a NWO camp, you will have a great trip.
Been there many times, N.pike 29.3 bs walleye 9.3 Fishing 6 times moose hunting 2 times . Class outfit. Vic and doug great peope goin to mink lake 9/4/15. let me know if you need info on sessi.
